1
00:01:32,120 --> 00:01:33,159
Greetings, Imperial Father.

2
00:01:35,640 --> 00:01:38,480
Why have you summoned your child?

3
00:01:40,560 --> 00:01:41,239
Take a look.

4
00:01:45,959 --> 00:01:46,519
Huai'an.

5
00:01:48,000 --> 00:01:48,719
Greetings, Imperial Father.

6
00:01:49,280 --> 00:01:51,120
Did you come to see Us for a reason?

7
00:01:51,680 --> 00:01:52,400
No reason.

8
00:01:52,879 --> 00:01:54,239
I just missed you, Imperial Father.

9
00:01:55,400 --> 00:01:56,159
You came at just the right time.

10
00:01:56,319 --> 00:01:57,480
We were thinking of you, too.

11
00:01:58,040 --> 00:01:59,239
Then let me rub your shoulders.

12
00:01:59,400 --> 00:02:00,200
Alright, come on.

13
00:02:06,760 --> 00:02:08,240
When His Majesty's children see him,

14
00:02:08,400 --> 00:02:09,840
they act like mice that have seen a cat.

15
00:02:10,000 --> 00:02:12,199
Only Princess Huai'an is cheerful,

16
00:02:12,280 --> 00:02:13,360
clever and lively,

17
00:02:13,560 --> 00:02:14,840
unafraid of His Majesty,

18
00:02:15,039 --> 00:02:17,400
and deeply favored by him.

19
00:02:20,919 --> 00:02:21,680
Have you finished reading?

20
00:02:23,719 --> 00:02:24,280
Imperial Father,

21
00:02:24,960 --> 00:02:25,719
Your child has finished reading.

22
00:02:26,400 --> 00:02:26,919
Speak, then.

23
00:02:28,479 --> 00:02:29,840
The Tuoluo Kingdom is poised to strike,

24
00:02:30,520 --> 00:02:32,800
intending to raid our southern border again.

25
00:02:33,199 --> 00:02:35,000
Do you have a way to counter it?

26
00:02:35,240 --> 00:02:35,759
Imperial Father,

27
00:02:36,520 --> 00:02:39,159
We've suffered repeated defeats recently.

28
00:02:39,439 --> 00:02:40,719
Nanxuan harbors ravenous ambition,

29
00:02:41,360 --> 00:02:43,199
Droughts and floods have left us drained.

30
00:02:43,360 --> 00:02:44,080
We are in no shape to fight.

31
00:02:45,240 --> 00:02:46,520
We should negotiate with Tuoluo

32
00:02:47,400 --> 00:02:48,280
and provide them with grain and supplies.

33
00:02:50,199 --> 00:02:51,599
Have you any brains at all?

34
00:02:52,360 --> 00:02:53,680
Nanxuan harbors ravenous ambition,

35
00:02:53,800 --> 00:02:55,639
but is Tuoluo any kinder?

36
00:02:55,759 --> 00:02:58,520
Supplying them means feeding a tiger.

37
00:02:59,080 --> 00:03:00,360
You are the Crown Prince,

38
00:03:00,560 --> 00:03:02,199
the model of the imperial family.

39
00:03:02,719 --> 00:03:05,120
Even if all court officials seek peace,

40
00:03:05,280 --> 00:03:06,199
you must not.

41
00:03:06,520 --> 00:03:08,240
Once backbone is lost,

42
00:03:08,360 --> 00:03:09,639
it can never be recovered.

43
00:03:09,919 --> 00:03:10,800
Yes, yes.

44
00:03:10,960 --> 00:03:12,319
Your child will heed your teachings.

45
00:03:12,680 --> 00:03:13,159
You...

46
00:03:13,479 --> 00:03:13,800
Imperial Father.

47
00:03:13,879 --> 00:03:14,280
You...

48
00:03:14,759 --> 00:03:15,199
Sit down, quickly.

49
00:03:15,360 --> 00:03:16,199
Please don't be angry.

50
00:03:16,800 --> 00:03:18,080
Royal Brother was thinking of the court,

51
00:03:18,280 --> 00:03:19,159
of the common people.

52
00:03:19,280 --> 00:03:20,319
Once war breaks out,

53
00:03:20,680 --> 00:03:21,919
winning leaves the people destitute,

54
00:03:22,240 --> 00:03:24,159
losing brings shame upon the court,

55
00:03:24,400 --> 00:03:25,240
and we lose cities and lands.

56
00:03:26,639 --> 00:03:27,439
Huai'an,

57
00:03:27,599 --> 00:03:29,080
you're still young, you don't understand.

58
00:03:29,319 --> 00:03:30,199
Right, right, I don't understand.

59
00:03:31,599 --> 00:03:32,439
Brother, please get up.

60
00:03:33,560 --> 00:03:34,639
Imperial Father, don't be angry anymore.

61
00:03:34,759 --> 00:03:37,039
General Chen has arrived.

62
00:03:44,240 --> 00:03:45,439
General, you have trouble walking.

63
00:03:45,759 --> 00:03:47,199
Dispense with such formalities.

64
00:03:47,719 --> 00:03:48,360
Yes, dispense with it.

65
00:03:51,080 --> 00:03:52,120
Thank you, Your Majesty.

66
00:03:52,840 --> 00:03:54,479
Old General, coming to see Us so late,

67
00:03:54,639 --> 00:03:55,639
what brings you here?

68
00:03:55,879 --> 00:03:56,520
Your Majesty,

69
00:03:56,800 --> 00:03:59,759
I have found a way to deal with Tuoluo.

70
00:04:13,960 --> 00:04:14,439
Crown Prince,

71
00:04:15,240 --> 00:04:15,800
take a look.

72
00:04:24,959 --> 00:04:25,600
General Chen,

73
00:04:26,240 --> 00:04:27,120
these methods of yours,

74
00:04:27,759 --> 00:04:28,600
did you devise them yourself?

75
00:04:28,839 --> 00:04:30,639
Your Highness,

76
00:04:31,160 --> 00:04:32,600
do you not trust me?

77
00:04:34,319 --> 00:04:35,000
Enough.

78
00:04:35,439 --> 00:04:37,519
We know exactly what you are capable of.

79
00:04:38,519 --> 00:04:41,120
Leading troops into battle, no question.

80
00:04:41,480 --> 00:04:42,759
But strategies like these

81
00:04:43,000 --> 00:04:44,399
aren't something you could come up with.

82
00:04:44,759 --> 00:04:45,439
Speak, then.

83
00:04:47,000 --> 00:04:48,000
Your Majesty is wise.

84
00:04:48,399 --> 00:04:49,120
In the last two days,

85
00:04:49,319 --> 00:04:51,519
I encountered a young prodigy.

86
00:04:51,639 --> 00:04:52,560
After hearing me describe

87
00:04:52,759 --> 00:04:55,240
the situation between us and Tuoluo,

88
00:04:55,439 --> 00:04:58,600
he quickly devised these countermeasures.

89
00:04:59,680 --> 00:05:02,199
The capital has such a gifted youth?

90
00:05:02,759 --> 00:05:05,279
What's his name? Where does he live?

91
00:05:05,680 --> 00:05:07,920
I dare not deceive Your Majesty.

92
00:05:08,279 --> 00:05:10,240
He is the Minister of Rites,

93
00:05:10,399 --> 00:05:11,720
Ning Ziming's fourth son,

94
00:05:12,000 --> 00:05:12,800
Ning Chen.

95
00:05:20,399 --> 00:05:21,720
As I recall, the Left Chancellor

96
00:05:22,040 --> 00:05:23,279
has only three grandsons.

97
00:05:24,720 --> 00:05:26,160
Your Highness may not know,

98
00:05:26,319 --> 00:05:29,399
Ning Chen is Ning Ziming's bastard son,

99
00:05:29,560 --> 00:05:31,319
only recently brought back home.

100
00:05:33,040 --> 00:05:35,680
I never thought that boy had such talent.

101
00:05:37,319 --> 00:05:37,920
Imperial Father,

102
00:05:38,519 --> 00:05:39,959
do you happen to know Ning Chen?

103
00:05:40,720 --> 00:05:42,639
Did you read the poem We sent you?

104
00:05:43,879 --> 00:05:45,079
Wasn't it signed by Lan Xing?

105
00:05:46,120 --> 00:05:48,079
Could Ning Chen be Lan Xing?

106
00:05:50,439 --> 00:05:52,279
So it was Your Majesty at Zhuangyuan Tower

107
00:05:52,399 --> 00:05:54,040
who bought this boy's poem.

108
00:05:54,680 --> 00:05:55,199
Excellent.

109
00:05:55,680 --> 00:05:56,240
Excellent indeed!

110
00:05:58,759 --> 00:05:59,240
Your Majesty,

111
00:05:59,959 --> 00:06:01,680
Ning Chen is well-versed in poetry,

112
00:06:02,000 --> 00:06:03,680
and understands military strategy.

113
00:06:03,800 --> 00:06:05,480
Such talent is truly rare.

114
00:06:05,639 --> 00:06:06,480
With proper cultivation,

115
00:06:06,680 --> 00:06:08,680
he will surely achieve greatness.

116
00:06:08,959 --> 00:06:11,439
I never expected old General Chen

117
00:06:11,560 --> 00:06:13,160
to praise this youth so highly.

118
00:06:13,639 --> 00:06:14,279
We recall

119
00:06:14,360 --> 00:06:17,079
you've never praised the Crown Prince so.

120
00:06:19,160 --> 00:06:19,879
Well...

121
00:06:20,199 --> 00:06:21,680
Your Majesty may not know,

122
00:06:22,639 --> 00:06:25,480
the capital has grown idle these years.

123
00:06:25,720 --> 00:06:28,160
The young men are all soft and feeble.

124
00:06:28,360 --> 00:06:31,040
They should toughen up on the battlefield.

125
00:06:33,279 --> 00:06:33,920
Your Highness,

126
00:06:34,240 --> 00:06:35,560
I'm not referring to you.

127
00:06:39,720 --> 00:06:40,319
Your Majesty,

128
00:06:41,000 --> 00:06:44,639
a promising talent like Ning Chen

129
00:06:44,800 --> 00:06:45,800
must not go to waste.

130
00:06:48,040 --> 00:06:49,240
But based on just one poem

131
00:06:49,600 --> 00:06:50,759
and a few strategies,

132
00:06:51,040 --> 00:06:52,000
entrusting him with great responsibility

133
00:06:52,600 --> 00:06:53,519
would be premature.

134
00:06:54,399 --> 00:06:55,439
The boy is still young.

135
00:06:55,879 --> 00:06:57,000
Let's test him a few more times.

136
00:06:58,959 --> 00:06:59,959
I never imagined the capital

137
00:07:00,399 --> 00:07:01,759
had such an extraordinary youth.

138
00:07:02,199 --> 00:07:02,639
Imperial Father,

139
00:07:03,240 --> 00:07:04,560
Your child is quite intrigued.

140
00:07:04,839 --> 00:07:05,759
Could you arrange for me

141
00:07:06,040 --> 00:07:07,079
to meet him in person?

142
00:07:07,279 --> 00:07:08,680
The Crown Prince may be indecisive,

143
00:07:08,959 --> 00:07:10,720
but in judging and employing men,

144
00:07:11,000 --> 00:07:12,279
he takes after Us.

145
00:07:13,439 --> 00:07:14,480
What's the use of meeting him?

146
00:07:14,879 --> 00:07:17,879
Such great talent isn't easily won over.

147
00:07:20,319 --> 00:07:20,920
Imperial Father,

148
00:07:21,480 --> 00:07:22,319
you and the old General

149
00:07:22,480 --> 00:07:23,800
have praised Ning Chen so highly,

150
00:07:24,120 --> 00:07:25,399
I want to meet him too.

151
00:07:26,120 --> 00:07:27,120
You want to meet him too?

152
00:07:27,920 --> 00:07:28,560
Very well.

153
00:07:29,480 --> 00:07:31,600
But Ning Chen doesn't know Our identity.

154
00:07:32,319 --> 00:07:33,079
Old General,

155
00:07:33,480 --> 00:07:34,920
We'll trouble you to arrange it.

156
00:07:35,519 --> 00:07:35,920
This...

157
00:07:36,319 --> 00:07:36,839
Your Majesty,

158
00:07:37,240 --> 00:07:39,360
Ning Chen doesn't know my identity either.

159
00:07:40,199 --> 00:07:40,639
You...

160
00:07:40,800 --> 00:07:42,680
I went out drinking,

161
00:07:43,000 --> 00:07:44,040
forgot to bring silver,

162
00:07:44,240 --> 00:07:45,759
and was beaten by the tavern boys.

163
00:07:45,959 --> 00:07:47,399
He passed by and saved me.

164
00:07:47,680 --> 00:07:48,800
The amusing part is,

165
00:07:48,959 --> 00:07:50,399
he had no money on him either.

166
00:07:50,560 --> 00:07:52,759
He just took the beating in my place.

167
00:07:52,959 --> 00:07:55,160
Which shows his kind heart.

168
00:07:56,399 --> 00:07:57,759
What shall We do then?

169
00:07:58,360 --> 00:08:00,120
If he learns of Our identity,

170
00:08:00,360 --> 00:08:02,720
he'll inevitably try to curry favor.

171
00:08:03,360 --> 00:08:04,160
Such a pure heart

172
00:08:04,319 --> 00:08:07,199
shouldn't be tainted by power too soon.

173
00:08:08,279 --> 00:08:08,800
Your Majesty,

174
00:08:09,279 --> 00:08:10,879
I have an idea.

175
00:08:11,079 --> 00:08:13,360
Given Ning Chen's current situation,

176
00:08:13,519 --> 00:08:15,160
he urgently needs silver.

177
00:08:15,680 --> 00:08:16,720
Since he can write poetry,

178
00:08:16,879 --> 00:08:18,759
he'll surely return to Zhuangyuan Tower

179
00:08:19,360 --> 00:08:20,279
to sell his poems.

180
00:08:20,720 --> 00:08:22,160
We can wait for him there.

181
00:08:24,759 --> 00:08:25,279
Very well.

182
00:08:25,959 --> 00:08:26,439
Crown Prince,

183
00:08:26,759 --> 00:08:27,360
tomorrow,

184
00:08:27,680 --> 00:08:29,759
you shall come with Us to see him.

185
00:08:30,439 --> 00:08:31,120
Thank you, Imperial Father.

186
00:08:32,159 --> 00:08:33,039
I really want to see

187
00:08:33,159 --> 00:08:35,159
what that little brat looks like.

188
00:08:37,840 --> 00:08:39,799
We almost forgot about Huai'an.

189
00:08:40,039 --> 00:08:42,039
You shall come with Us as well.

190
00:08:42,559 --> 00:08:43,080
Long live Imperial Father!

191
00:08:48,360 --> 00:08:48,879
Mother!

192
00:08:49,279 --> 00:08:50,879
Why did Father bring that bastard again?

193
00:08:51,360 --> 00:08:52,639
Then everything we did before

194
00:08:53,039 --> 00:08:54,320
will all have been for nothing!

195
00:08:58,159 --> 00:08:59,559
I didn't think it through before.

196
00:09:00,000 --> 00:09:01,240
I didn't anticipate public criticism.

197
00:09:02,360 --> 00:09:03,440
But the three of you, rest assured.

198
00:09:03,840 --> 00:09:05,080
Even if he lives in the Ning residence,

199
00:09:05,480 --> 00:09:07,080
a bastard will always be a bastard.

200
00:09:07,759 --> 00:09:08,679
The Ning family estate

201
00:09:09,000 --> 00:09:10,200
will belong to you three brothers.

202
00:09:10,360 --> 00:09:11,159
No one can take it away.

203
00:09:12,879 --> 00:09:13,440
Mother,

204
00:09:14,440 --> 00:09:15,679
about this matter,

205
00:09:16,039 --> 00:09:18,240
if General Chen takes it to His Majesty,

206
00:09:18,679 --> 00:09:20,639
will it affect my imperial exams?

207
00:09:21,200 --> 00:09:22,080
Don't worry.

208
00:09:23,279 --> 00:09:24,679
Your father and grandfather

209
00:09:24,840 --> 00:09:25,879
have already suppressed this matter.

210
00:09:27,000 --> 00:09:27,759
However,

211
00:09:28,279 --> 00:09:29,679
this General Chen,

212
00:09:30,320 --> 00:09:31,639
how on earth did he get to know him?

213
00:09:33,080 --> 00:09:33,840
Do you know?

214
00:09:34,440 --> 00:09:35,399
We don't know, Mother.

215
00:09:35,919 --> 00:09:36,919
When we got to Xiaomei's home,

216
00:09:37,120 --> 00:09:37,840
that old wretch...

217
00:09:38,600 --> 00:09:39,399
that old general

218
00:09:39,840 --> 00:09:40,960
was already sitting inside.

219
00:09:42,960 --> 00:09:45,600
If that bastard clings to General Chen,

220
00:09:45,720 --> 00:09:46,639
what shall we do?

221
00:09:47,559 --> 00:09:48,039
That's right.

222
00:09:48,559 --> 00:09:49,279
Xiaomei...

223
00:09:51,600 --> 00:09:52,120
Xing'er,

224
00:09:52,960 --> 00:09:54,519
right now he only cares about Xiaomei.

225
00:09:55,159 --> 00:09:56,240
Send someone to watch her house.

226
00:09:56,759 --> 00:09:58,120
She might come in handy later.

227
00:10:01,200 --> 00:10:02,279
I have to go by myself?

228
00:10:03,320 --> 00:10:04,759
Your eldest brother will soon take office.

229
00:10:05,039 --> 00:10:06,080
He can't afford any trouble.

230
00:10:06,600 --> 00:10:08,080
Your third brother is injured.

231
00:10:08,480 --> 00:10:10,039
If you won't go, I will.

232
00:10:10,440 --> 00:10:10,879
I'll...

233
00:10:14,000 --> 00:10:14,720
go.

234
00:10:16,759 --> 00:10:17,279
Second son,

235
00:10:17,480 --> 00:10:18,919
Xiaomei is just a frail woman.

236
00:10:19,440 --> 00:10:21,320
If she proves useful against Ning Chen,

237
00:10:21,799 --> 00:10:23,320
you will have done a great deed.

238
00:10:24,200 --> 00:10:24,679
I...

239
00:10:26,200 --> 00:10:27,279
perhaps your grandfather

240
00:10:27,759 --> 00:10:29,120
will see you in a new light.

241
00:10:31,320 --> 00:10:32,360
I'll go, I'll go!

242
00:11:23,360 --> 00:11:24,679
Come, Huai'an, give me one.

243
00:11:27,960 --> 00:11:28,559
Good, good, good.

244
00:11:54,200 --> 00:11:55,960
It's been several days now.

245
00:11:56,360 --> 00:11:57,639
Could it be that boy

246
00:11:58,080 --> 00:11:59,360
hasn't recovered from his injuries?

247
00:12:00,879 --> 00:12:02,720
Looks like we waited in vain today.

248
00:12:03,559 --> 00:12:04,039
Let's go.

249
00:12:06,000 --> 00:12:06,360
Your Majesty...

250
00:12:06,440 --> 00:12:07,559
No, no, no, Master Bi.

251
00:12:07,919 --> 00:12:08,519
He's here!

